                        <summary>1 copy of Dastūr-nāmah Kisrá, translated from  Arabic by  Ṭabāṭabāyī </summary>



                        <msItem xml:id="R_13_68-item1">



                            <author key="person_f407" role="aut" change="#role-assignment">
